      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " The heathens esteemed fornication either no sin, or a very little one; but adultery was heinous and formidable even among the heathens, and especially here, because it was fresh in memory how sorely God had punished Abimelech, and all his family, only for an intention of adultery, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bldvs",
        "text": " Genesis 20:1-18",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
